00:30:26,559 --> 00:30:28,880
Your Majesty,
it's Xu Hour. They haven't arrived.

295
00:30:29,920 --> 00:30:31,160
Be patient. Wait longer.

296
00:30:31,799 --> 00:30:32,240
Does

297
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:33,880
Know-It-All really know

298
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:35,119
the whereabouts

299
00:30:35,119 --> 00:30:35,880
of the treasure?

300
00:30:37,319 --> 00:30:38,680
