301
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:39,720
These people

302
00:30:39,960 --> 00:30:41,640
are well connected with vast influence.

303
00:30:42,240 --> 00:30:43,400
From the lower echelons

304
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:44,759
to the upper reaches,

305
00:30:45,359 --> 00:30:46,440
