306
00:30:47,440 --> 00:30:48,119
Consort Liu

307
00:30:48,279 --> 00:30:49,680
secretly left the palace earlier.

308
00:30:50,359 --> 00:30:51,359
I relied on them

309
00:30:51,559 --> 00:30:52,839
to obtain precise information.

310
00:31:11,119 --> 00:31:11,839
Hero Duan.

311
00:31:17,319 --> 00:31:17,839
Sir.

312
00:31:19,319 --> 00:31:19,720
Please.

313
00:31:34,319 --> 00:31:35,000
It's cold.

314
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:36,599
Drink some wine to warm up.

315
00:31:37,799 --> 00:31:38,240
No need.

316
00:31:39,552 --> 00:31:42,020
(Duan Zhixing, Emperor of Dali)

317
00:31:51,079 --> 00:31:52,000
What request

318
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:54,240
do you have today?

319
00:31:56,119 --> 00:31:57,680
The Nine Yin True Sutra.

320
00:32:02,519 --> 00:32:03,880
You seek the Sutra too?

321
00:32:07,599 --> 00:32:10,240
In the martial world,

322
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:12,880
who doesn't crave supremacy?

323
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,799
This is no trivial matter.

324
00:32:16,279 --> 00:32:17,119
So

325
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:18,839
I need you,

326
00:32:19,400 --> 00:32:20,400
Mr. Know-It-All.

327
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:22,400
Rumors say

328
00:32:22,759 --> 00:32:23,880
the Jin family of Xiliang

329
00:32:23,880 --> 00:32:25,279
got the Sutra and were slaughtered,

330
00:32:25,759 --> 00:32:26,960
leaving only a girl

331
00:32:27,160 --> 00:32:28,279
who knows its whereabouts.

332
00:32:28,400 --> 00:32:30,400
They call her the Living Map.

333
00:32:32,519 --> 00:32:33,279
This is true.

334
00:32:33,799 --> 00:32:35,359
Huang Yaoshi of Taohua Island

335
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:36,440
took this girl across

336
00:32:37,359 --> 00:32:38,079
the Song lands.

337
00:32:41,119 --> 00:32:41,960
That's true.

338
00:32:42,480 --> 00:32:44,319
But that was

339
00:32:45,079 --> 00:32:46,359
over ten days ago.

340
00:32:50,559 --> 00:32:51,480
I need the Living Map's

341
00:32:51,519 --> 00:32:53,119
current location

342
00:32:54,119 --> 00:32:54,839
and route.

343
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,160
Name your price.

344
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:02,640
No price today.

345
00:33:04,880 --> 00:33:05,319
Why?

346
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,119
When the deed is done,

347
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:10,720
we can both name exorbitant prices.

348
00:33:12,079 --> 00:33:13,119
You cripple!

349
00:33:14,119 --> 00:33:15,359
Can't even handle simple work.

350
00:33:17,720 --> 00:33:18,759
In less than half a month,

351
00:33:19,279 --> 00:33:21,200
you've broken so many bowls.

352
00:33:23,119 --> 00:33:24,039
I'll compensate you.

353
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:25,640
With what?

354
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:27,079
You're a beggar

355
00:33:27,079 --> 00:33:28,359
and refugee from Nanzhao.

356
00:33:28,559 --> 00:33:29,400
You're broke

357
00:33:29,640 --> 00:33:30,599
with wages docked.

358
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:31,519
How will you repay?

359
00:33:35,559 --> 00:33:36,279
Why staring at me?

360
00:33:36,680 --> 00:33:38,200
I hold your indenture contract.

361
00:33:38,359 --> 00:33:39,519
I can beat you if I please.

362
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:41,640
Your worthless life belongs to me.

363
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:44,759
Over trivial matters,

364
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:46,640
you rage like thunder.

365
00:33:47,079 --> 00:33:48,359
Spouting nonsense still?

366
00:33:48,640 --> 00:33:49,839
Daring to curse me?

367
00:33:50,319 --> 00:33:51,440
You pedantic scholar

368
00:33:51,559 --> 00:33:52,559
and stray dog!

369
00:33:52,799 --> 00:33:53,839
You're useful at nothing,

370
00:33:53,839 --> 00:33:55,000
worse than a stinking beggar!

371
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:56,319
You're the stray dog!

372
00:33:59,000 --> 00:33:59,440
What?

373
00:34:00,160 --> 00:34:01,000
Am I wrong?

374
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:03,119
If I hadn't taken you in

375
00:34:03,319 --> 00:34:04,400
and given you food

376
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:05,559
and shelter,

377
00:34:05,680 --> 00:34:06,559
