378
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:11,360
Did I disturb you, sir?

379
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:13,079
Sorry. I was just...

380
00:34:17,559 --> 00:34:18,159
Young friend,

381
00:34:19,119 --> 00:34:20,159
