390
00:34:41,639 --> 00:34:42,519
My master

391
00:34:42,719 --> 00:34:43,840
is a hero from Dali

392
00:34:44,400 --> 00:34:45,519
who vanquishes evil.

393
00:34:46,239 --> 00:34:47,039
This young man

394
00:34:47,360 --> 00:34:48,320
is our compatriot.

395
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:50,199
If you harm him again,

396
00:34:51,039 --> 00:34:51,880
I'll make you pay.

397
00:34:52,079 --> 00:34:52,760
Understood?

398
00:34:53,679 --> 00:34:54,440
Yes.

399
00:34:54,719 --> 00:34:55,639
Understood.

400
00:34:58,639 --> 00:34:59,519
Take care.

401
00:35:20,760 --> 00:35:21,536
Your Majesty.

402
00:35:22,239 --> 00:35:22,760
Well?

403
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:25,280
I've asked

404
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:25,840
