405
00:35:26,719 --> 00:35:28,039
That man does come from Dali.

406
00:35:28,840 --> 00:35:30,079
His family perished in the war.

407
00:35:30,719 --> 00:35:31,760
To survive,

408
00:35:32,079 --> 00:35:33,119
he works at this tavern.

409
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:35,360
The man who beat him

410
00:35:35,719 --> 00:35:36,760
is the tavern's steward.

411
00:35:38,119 --> 00:35:40,079
Not only does he bully him regularly

412
00:35:40,760 --> 00:35:42,079
and seized his books,

413
00:35:42,639 --> 00:35:43,880
but he also took the memento

414
00:35:44,159 --> 00:35:45,079
left by his family,

415
00:35:45,800 --> 00:35:46,480
two bracelets.

416
00:35:47,519 --> 00:35:49,880
Your Majesty,
why do you show such concern

417
00:35:50,239 --> 00:35:51,280
for this man?

418
00:35:55,840 --> 00:35:56,559
He

419
00:36:00,039 --> 00:36:01,199
has a scholar's integrity.

420
00:36:23,599 --> 00:36:26,639
Where did you get these bracelets?

421
00:36:29,679 --> 00:36:30,480
Gao Dafu

422
00:36:31,519 --> 00:36:32,239
and Gao Yang

423
00:36:33,199 --> 00:36:34,880
were your father and brother?

424
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:38,440
Yes.

425
00:36:44,519 --> 00:36:45,880
When warriors in Dali's army

426
00:36:46,400 --> 00:36:47,480
head to battle,

427
00:36:48,400 --> 00:36:49,800
they wear iron rings engraved

428
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:51,599
with their names on their wrists

429
00:36:54,199 --> 00:36:55,840
to ensure identification

430
00:36:56,079 --> 00:36:56,960
if their faces

431
00:36:58,079 --> 00:36:59,159
are disfigured in battle.

432
00:37:06,119 --> 00:37:07,199
In Dali, there's a rule:

433
00:37:07,320 --> 00:37:09,119
for those who die in battle,
their families

434
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:10,360
are exempt

435
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:12,039
from taxes and corvée labor.

436
00:37:12,719 --> 00:37:14,119
There'll be burial assistance.

437
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:16,679
Their widows and children
will have pensions.

438
00:37:17,519 --> 00:37:18,280
So why

439
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,840
did you become a refugee?

440
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,400
Our lands were destroyed.

441
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,360
Homes collapsed.

442
00:37:30,679 --> 00:37:32,280
And even livestock perished.

443
00:37:33,559 --> 00:37:35,239
Amidst the ruins,

444
00:37:36,480 --> 00:37:37,800
there was no preferential care.

445
00:37:44,519 --> 00:37:45,599
They sacrifice their lives,

446
00:37:47,320 --> 00:37:48,599
yet receive no dignity.

447
00:37:57,679 --> 00:37:58,440
Thank you, sir.

448
00:37:59,239 --> 00:38:00,639
I was rude earlier.

449
00:38:01,920 --> 00:38:02,760
May I ask

450
00:38:03,159 --> 00:38:04,519
