451
00:38:07,320 --> 00:38:08,000
Never mind that.

452
00:38:09,199 --> 00:38:09,519
Here.

453
00:38:13,159 --> 00:38:14,079
Your indenture.

454
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:16,079
I've bought it back

455
00:38:16,719 --> 00:38:17,400
