460
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:28,599
Here.

461
00:38:30,079 --> 00:38:31,000
Keep the indenture.

462
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:32,960
This bundle contains

463
00:38:33,079 --> 00:38:34,320
