464
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:35,480
Take them.

465
00:38:36,239 --> 00:38:36,880
Return to Dali.

466
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:56,480
Sir,

467
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:58,360
I'm Gao Ang,

468
00:38:58,840 --> 00:39:00,320
from Dali's Lanchang County.

469
00:39:01,679 --> 00:39:03,559
Years of border wars

470
00:39:04,480 --> 00:39:06,280
reached our doorstep.

471
00:39:07,119 --> 00:39:08,079
All my family

472
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:10,199
perished.

473
00:39:11,159 --> 00:39:12,159
My right leg

474
00:39:13,400 --> 00:39:14,679
was stamped

475
00:39:14,679 --> 00:39:15,360
by warhorses.

476
00:39:16,400 --> 00:39:17,760
Hence this limp.

477
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:19,760
But I assure you,

478
00:39:20,559 --> 00:39:21,440
