479
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:22,800
or groom,

480
00:39:23,480 --> 00:39:24,599
I'll do any dirty

481
00:39:24,599 --> 00:39:25,440
or hard work.

482
00:39:26,199 --> 00:39:27,840
Since you hold my indenture,

483
00:39:28,400 --> 00:39:29,280
from this day forth,

484
00:39:29,559 --> 00:39:30,199
