486
00:39:37,719 --> 00:39:38,239
Rise.

487
00:39:39,119 --> 00:39:39,719
Rise now.

488
00:39:44,519 --> 00:39:46,039
This was a small favor.

489
00:39:46,519 --> 00:39:47,800
And I need no servants

490
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:48,480
