491
00:39:50,199 --> 00:39:51,679
Do you find me useless, sir?

492
00:39:53,159 --> 00:39:54,119
I didn't mean that.

493
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,199
But why

494
00:39:55,360 --> 00:39:56,400
