504
00:40:38,239 --> 00:40:39,679
A very important piece of news.

505
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:41,760
Once the news arrives,

506
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:42,880
I'll depart.

507
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:44,840
So you've accepted me?

508
00:40:50,719 --> 00:40:51,360
I guess so.

